German Government Considering Euro Bonds, Sueddeutsche Reports

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-08-16T06:53:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-16/german-government-considering-euro-bonds-sueddeutsche-reports.html
German Chancellor  Angela Merkel  is
examining whether joint euro bonds could help end the sovereign
debt crisis,  Sueddeutsche Zeitung  reported without quoting
anyone.  Merkel may discuss the subject when she meets French
President Nicolas Sarkozy later today, while it was not
officially on the agenda, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt 
